uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:13:08.000Z","msg":"搞會員大會<br />\n唔洗申請<br />\n全港市民自動入會"},{"pid":"5618873dd3575f080a3c4659b15c075b1c001c6f","tid":237170,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:14:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成個post 完全冇人鬧林鄭鬧政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實林鄭未上台關林鄭咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔見689惡撚到話林鄭嗡乜春都係7月1號之後既事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2af38e68fd70266c877179d35325fa8433208a","tid":237170,"uid":106259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:14:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5f1e80981b85cd4efb74cc19c452fb196f5b491","tid":237170,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:15:54.000Z","msg":"唔屌港共屌民陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家連集會遊行，港共都要攪動作玩封殺，日後你班柒頭上網發噏風，都可能俾港共出陰招攪你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ecaf20bf700ac22d102c22882b8e2bfffe69eb","tid":237170,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:16:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9 架d留言 民陣係抵屌 <br />\n但點計都屌柒共狗先啦 你地班五毛/假膠垃圾個老母仲撚抵屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泛民係賣港賊，扮反對派，特別係民主黨<br />\n我依家一定會屌柒依班人先"},{"pid":"5962681e5cc52c59b7d3aa81d2354f55e50bb6b7","tid":237170,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:17:28.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0036c20eedbe2da0bc5a2a3eb5e7a0905e644f5","tid":237170,"uid":36014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:18:34.000Z","msg":"呢鋪我撐689<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2561f928523eb7c445f9baf4a11bf2